en_425406_0	The annual Perahera Festival of the Sabaragamu Maha Saman Devale commenced yesterday.
en_425406_1	The first Kumbal Perahera paraded the streets yesterday while a large crowd gathered to witness the Perahera.
en_425406_2	The Saman Dev Puda Varna 2019 Perahera Festival commenced on the 31 of last month with the planting of Kap.
en_425406_3	The first Kumbal Perahera commenced yesterday while it is scheduled to be held until the 08th of this month.
en_425406_4	The Perahera of the Esala Perahera Festival parading the streets will commence on the 09th of this month and continue until the 13th.
en_425406_5	Thereafter the Randoli Perahera is slated to be held.
en_425406_6	The Perahera Festival will draw to a close with the conduct of the day Perahera after the water cutting festival on the 14th of this month.
en_425406_7	The devotional media contribution of this Perahera Festival is being made by the Independent Television Media Network.
